1.  Executive Summary 
 
SpecTec is transitioning from a traditional Annual Maintenance Fee (AMF) support model to a structured Customer Success support package framework. This transition is designed to: 
 
 
 
Increase predictable recurring revenue 
 
Align support effort to customer value 
 
Support proactive Customer Success engagement 
 
Improve operational scalability 
 
Enable advisory-led service growth 
 
Increase Professional Services opportunity generation 
 
Support long-term SaaS maturity 
 
 
 
 
 
From Reactive Software Maintenance → Managed Operational Customer Success Services 
 
 
 
The proposed pricing model is designed to balance commercial growth, customer retention, operational maturity, market competitiveness, and long-term scalability. 
 
 
 
